<span class="site">．中新网</span><span>&#91;引用日期2018-10-13&#93;</span></li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type1 " id="reference-[2]-5833579-wrap">
<span class="index">2.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_2_5833579" id="refIndex_2_5833579" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[2]_5833579">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<a rel="nofollow" href="/reference/9381/964cVNWM8jk-krEE80nST6g4ReAD--5LED4-uPJ3mB6_frKveBCqyIUwaYZFtwjzNq4a6xP7wgtaDk8q_1jxSLQL1Ma3CqrOszWAM7mGkdwh0hN5NnSv" target="_blank" class="text">冬至大如年！中国人不得不知的冬至民俗起源<span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a>
